snippet: Ozzie Guillen, a former White Sox manager, was back in Chicago as his new club, the Marlins, took on the Cubs.
abstract: MLB Roundup; Ozzie Guillen, former Chicago White Sox manager, returns to Chicago to witness his new club, the Miami Marlins, crush the White Sox, 9-5; other MLB results noted.
lead_paragraph: Ozzie Guillen, a former White Sox manager, was back in Chicago as his new club, the Marlins, took on the Cubs.

headline.main: Guillen Makes Return to a City That He Loves but Had to Leave
headline.print_headline: Guillen Makes Return to a City That He Loves but Had to Leave
